Insta: https://www.instagram.com/realfoltyn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

Tila nag-iba ang mga kilos mo at salita
Bakit kaya? Parang hindi ka na masaya
Ika'y biglang natauhan
Umalis kaagad nang hindi nagpapaalam
Ang sabi ko hindi kita mamimiss
Hanggang kailan ito matitiis?
Ika'y biglang natauhan
Umalis kaagad nang wala man lang paalam
'Pag nawala, doon lang mamimiss

Alam ko na, magaling lang ako sa umpisa
Umasa ka pa sa akin

snippet.title: " LIHIM, LUPA AT LABAN !! "  AUG. 11, 2025 | FPJ's Batang Quiapo ADVANCE Trailer Episode645
snippet.description:
Sa gitna ng lumalagablab na digmaan ng pamilya, kapangyarihan, at katotohanan, tumindig ang mga bayani ng karaniwang tao. Si Marites, isang anak na handang ialay ang lahat para sa pamilya. Si Tindeng at Alfredo, simbolo ng tibay ng puso sa kabila ng pagkakagapos. Si Tanggol, ang kandidatong hindi binili ng sistema—kundi pinanday ng prinsipyo.

Samantalang lumulubog sa sarili niyang galit at paghihiganti si Pilar, unti-unti namang nabubunyag ang mga madidilim na lihim ng pamilyang Guerrero—mga lihim na maaaring bumagsak sa buong lungsod.

Sa bawat putok ng baril, sa bawat sampal, sa bawat suntok—lumalantad ang mga tunay na kulay ng mga taong dati’y may maskara. At sa likod ng ingay ng karahasan, naririnig ang bulong ng pag-asa: na sa gitna ng dilim, may mga pusong patuloy na lumalaban para sa tama.

ito ay isang teleseryeng puno ng paninindigan, rebelasyon, at pagmamahal, na magpapaalala sa atin:
Ang kapangyarihan ay lilipas, ngunit ang katotohanan ay mananatili.

snippet.description:
"One-Punch Man” returns with Season 3! Check out the latest trailer for the continuation of this series!

Saitama is a hero who only became a hero for fun. After three years of “special training,” he’s become so strong that he’s practically invincible. In fact, he’s too strong—even his mightiest opponents are taken out with a single punch. Alongside Genos, his faithful disciple, Saitama performs his official hero duties as a member of the Hero Association. One day, monsters claiming to be from the Monster Association suddenly appeared, taking a child of Hero Association executive hostage. The S-class heroes gather and plan a raid on the Monster Association hideout to rescue the hostage. Meanwhile, Garou, a “human monster” who was taken by the Monster Association during a battle with the heroes, awakens in the Monster Association hideout."

snippet.title: Good Boy - Official Trailer | HD | IFC Films
snippet.description:
Indy, a loyal golden-brown retriever, follows his owner Todd to an aging farmhouse tucked deep in the countryside. But the walls whisper, the shadows breathe, and something unseen has already claimed the place. Todd is blind to the horrors curling around them — but Indy can see. Through the dog’s eyes, the world twists into a nightmare of flickering visions and lurking shapes. Bound by unshakable loyalty, Indy stands between his human and the darkness, ready to face the things no one else can see.

Concept Trailer

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
